<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Invariant Foundation | The Determinism Standard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav style="padding: 32px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
    <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">
      INVARIANT.
    </div>
    <a href="#ecosystem" style="color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none; font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 600;">
      THE STANDARD &#8594;
    </a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark" style="min-height: 80vh; display: flex; align-items: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="title-monolith">THE ERA OF SPECULATION IS DEAD.</h1>
      <h1 class="title-monolith" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">MATHEMATICS IS THE NEW STANDARD.</h1>
      
      <div style="margin-top: 64px; display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="#manifesto" class="btn-brutal">Read The Manifesto</a>
        <a href="#ecosystem" class="btn-brutal" style="background-color: var(--text-primary); color: var(--bg-primary);">Enter The Core</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Manifesto Section -->
  <section id="manifesto" class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="title-monolith" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);">WE REPLACE THE CASINO WITH DETERMINISM.</h2>
      <p class="text-stark" style="color: var(--bg-secondary); margin-top: 32px; font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 900px;">
        The current digital and financial architectures are built on a foundation of sand—narrative, emotion, and manipulation. 
        Invariant is the architectural foundation of the future. We do not gamble. We do not speculate. We execute mathematical truth.
        If you are relying on narrative, you are already obsolete.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecosystem Section -->
  <section id="ecosystem" class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">THE VANGUARD</h2>
      <h3 class="title-monolith" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);">THE DETERMINISTIC ECOSYSTEM</h3>
      
      <div class="bento-grid">
        <a href="https://dwtl.io" class="bento-card">
          <div>
            <h4 class="card-title">Axiom Core</h4>
            <p class="card-desc">Financial Determinism & Market Truth. The engine that strips emotion from the tape.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>INITIATE</span><span>&#8594;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://lumev.tlid.io" class="bento-card">
          <div>
            <h4 class="card-title">Lume-V</h4>
            <p class="card-desc">The Deterministic Ecosystem Standard. Replacing subjective infrastructure with verifiable truth.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>INITIATE</span><span>&#8594;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="bento-card">
          <div>
            <h4 class="card-title">Meridian</h4>
            <p class="card-desc">Trustless Identity & State. The foundational layer for an uncorrupted digital society.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>INITIATE</span><span>&#8594;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="bento-card">
          <div>
            <h4 class="card-title">Hydrocore</h4>
            <p class="card-desc">Autonomous Resource Management. Algorithmic allocation without human bottleneck.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>INITIATE</span><span>&#8594;</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="bento-card">
          <div>
            <h4 class="card-title">Lume42</h4>
            <p class="card-desc">Advanced R&D and AI Agents. Expanding the frontier of deterministic automation.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span>INITIATE</span><span>&#8594;</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="section section-dark" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 900; font-size: 2rem; letter-spacing: -0.05em; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        INVARIANT.
      </div>
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--text-secondary);">
        &copy; 2026 The Determinism Standard. All Rights Reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
